Invocation Name: date tracker
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This is a tool for you to look up popular public holidays and know how many days are left until a specific event. Some holidays may not be listed as this is based around the global calendar. If you would like a holiday to be added, leave a review and I'll add your event. Please note that I will not add events like personal birthdays. There's also an easter egg that I'll let you find.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
